h=616 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A typical adventure can be completed in 30–90 minutes, depending on the complexity level of your choice. Just like a game of chess, Words of Yendor offers endless replayability, providing unique and thrilling adventures each time you play.<br></li><li>Your progress is automatically saved, allowing you to contemplate the challenges for as long as you like. The game remains unaffected by the passage of real time.<br></li><li>Note that embracing the spirit of roguelikes, this is also a “permadeath” game, so if your hero falls, the game is over. However, if you enter the same <i>adventure seed</i> number, you can replay any adventure as many times as you want.<br></li><li>It's never just one of the “red, green, blue” endings. Each one is personal and unique!</li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/1c76cba0edeaf214cc8e60568ea129d8.poster.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/1c76cba0edeaf214cc8e60568ea129d8.webm?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/1c76cba0edeaf214cc8e60568ea129d8.mp4?t=1765744245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/13dbcf0081c929f9d63ac13ff626b136.avif?t=1765744245\" width=616 height=141 /></span></p>",
